// Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-5225 — Mass File Rename (reynolds)
// Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 51992252-9812-5baa-ad99-9a06b7f92149

#event_simpleName=*
| (FilePath = *.encrypted OR FilePath = *.locked OR FilePath = *.ransom)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
